OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with showery rain, some heavy
OL,7,Fand perhaps thundery at first.
OL,8,FOvernight becoming drier with more
OL,9,Fscattered showers, and the odd clear
OL,10,Finterval.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny
OL,13,Fintervals but also a few showers,
OL,14,Fwhich could turn heavy and thundery
OL,15,Fover Moray in the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,19,Fmix of bright spells and showers,
OL,20,Fthese heavy and thundery on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
